âš ï¸ Legal & Ethical Notice

This repository is intended only for:

Defensive security research

Firmware and protocol auditing

Simulation (SITL/HITL)

Testing on hardware you own or are authorized to use


ğŸš« This repository does not support:

RF jamming or interference

GPS spoofing against live systems

Unauthorized access or hijacking

Disruption of real-world aircraft


Always comply with applicable laws and regulations (FAA, FCC, EASA, CAA, etc.).


