Example Mermaid Diagrams

PX4 Secure Boot Chain

graph TD
A[Boot ROM] --> B[First-stage Bootloader]
B -->|Verify Signature| C[PX4 Firmware]
C --> D[PX4 Modules]
D --> E[Flight Tasks]

ArduPilot Data Flow & Trust Boundaries

graph LR
GCS[Ground Control Station] -->|MAVLink| FC[Flight Controller]
FC --> S[Sensor Fusion]
S --> N[Navigation]
N --> A[Actuators]
subgraph Trusted
FC
S
N
A
end

MAVLink Threat Surface (Defensive View)

graph LR
GCS -->|Signed MAVLink| FC
Attacker -.->|Unsigned / Replay| FC
FC -->|Reject & Log| LOGS[Security Logs]

Simulation vs Real-World Isolation

graph TD
SIM[Simulation Environment] -->|Virtual Links| SITL[SITL Autopilot]
SITL --> LOGS
REAL[Real Hardware] -.->|Physically Isolated| SIM


